title: Niche - a genetics survival game v1.0.3
description: Niche - a genetics survival game is a fresh blend of turn-based strategy and simulation combined with roguelike elements. Shape your own species of cat/fox/bear/dog-like animals based on real genetics. Keep your animals alive against all odds, such as hungry predators, climate change and spreading sickness. If your species goes extinct the game is lost and your evolution needs to start anew.Key Features:Real genetics for breeding systemOver 100 genes to shape your speciesProcedurally generated
